<h4>Neem Beauty Benefits</h4>
<strong><em>Can Treat Acne</em></strong>
<ul>
 	<li>Take a few neem leaves and boil them in water.</li>
 	<li>Dip a cotton ball into the water and then evenly rub it over your face.</li>
 	<li>You can also use a neem-yogurt or neem-cucumber facepack to reduce oiliness of your face.</li>
</ul>
