<strong><em>Can Treat Dry Skin</em></strong>
<ul>
 	<li>Take little amount of neem powder and add a few drops of grape seed oil.</li>
 	<li>Apply this paste to your face and leave it undisturbed for 15 minutes.</li>
 	<li>Wash with cold water.</li>
</ul>
<h2>2. Saffron</h2>
